1
00:00:06,700 --> 00:00:10,260
Mr. Shen put his faith
above all else in his life.

2
00:00:10,340 --> 00:00:11,739
He would die for his country

3
00:00:11,740 --> 00:00:13,620
without hesitation,

4
00:00:13,740 --> 00:00:17,019
yet when it comes to Miss Lin,
he is endlessly imperfect

5
00:00:17,020 --> 00:00:18,620
and full of helplessness.

6
00:00:19,020 --> 00:00:21,260
They were destined to meet,
but not to be together.

7
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:23,420
With all my heart,

8
00:00:23,780 --> 00:00:26,420
I pray to all the deities and Buddhas

9
00:00:26,940 --> 00:00:30,020
that Mr. Shen and Miss Lin

10
00:00:30,540 --> 00:00:32,260
meet again in the days to come.

11
00:00:33,100 --> 00:00:35,100
May they meet and not forget each other,

12
00:00:36,420 --> 00:00:38,940
continuing their love in the next life.

13
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:47,480
=Echoes of Gang City=

14
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:55,120
=Episode 28=
(Echoes of Gang City)

15
00:00:58,300 --> 00:00:59,739
Have the cargo ship to Gang City

16
00:00:59,740 --> 00:01:02,620
deliver this letter
to Shuyi in your name.

17
00:01:02,660 --> 00:01:04,859
You must hide your identity.

18
00:01:04,860 --> 00:01:05,980
Do not expose yourself.

19
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:07,660
Understood.

20
00:01:12,660 --> 00:01:14,219
Qianmo, here!

21
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:15,460
Right here.

22
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:16,619
Mr. Shen instructed

23
00:01:16,620 --> 00:01:18,139
that you must bring
back news of Miss Lin.

24
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:19,260
I will.

25
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:20,660
I'm leaving now.

26
00:01:23,620 --> 00:01:25,340
It's a must.

27
00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:27,700
It's a must.

28
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:29,819
Hurry up.

29
00:01:29,820 --> 00:01:31,140
Miss Lin!

30
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:34,340
Miss Lin.

31
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:35,939
Is there any news of Mr. Zhou?

32
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:38,020
Miss!

33
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:39,780
Miss!

34
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:41,700
- Miss!
- Madam Liu?

35
00:01:41,900 --> 00:01:43,540
Madam Liu, why are you here?

36
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:45,580
There is a letter for you.

37
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:50,200
(To Miss Lin)

38
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:53,059
Who... Who gave this to you?

39
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:55,180
It was Qianmo. Qianmo gave it to you.

40
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:02,739
(Miss, under Mr. Zhou's guidance,)

41
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:05,179
(I have made progress in my schoolwork.)

42
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:09,059
(But for some reason, Mr. Zhou
hasn't come to class for a week.)

43
00:02:09,060 --> 00:02:10,900
(It's really giving me a headache.)

44
00:02:12,220 --> 00:02:13,740
It's Shen Gu's handwriting.

45
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:17,620
This is bad.

46
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:19,660
We must evacuate this place immediately.

47
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:23,860
- Miss Lin went missing in Gang City.
- Miss...

48
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:28,620
We tried everything
and finally contacted her.

49
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:33,060
But it was still too late.

50
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:37,979
Miss Lin sacrificed herself
to protect the comrades' evacuation.

51
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:40,219
Shen Gu passed away.

52
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:44,060
Mr. Shen was also murdered.

53
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:51,460
Mr. Shen and Miss Lin never
found their happy ending, even in death.

54
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:55,660
Grandfather,

55
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,540
have you told me this story before?

56
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:02,019
When you were little and sick,
you always pestered me

57
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:03,540
to tell you stories.

58
00:03:04,020 --> 00:03:07,580
So I just took those past events

59
00:03:07,660 --> 00:03:09,660
and slowly told them to you as stories.

60
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:11,140
No wonder.

61
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,940
No wonder I always have this dream.

62
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,340
Don't cry.

63
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:21,739
Shen Gu.

64
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:22,540
Grandfather.

65
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:24,940
Where is your jade pendant?

66
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,180
Right here.

67
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:42,780
This is the jade pendant
I lost in Gang City all those years ago.

68
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:45,940
Not only did it save your life,

69
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:48,140
but it also saved mine.

70
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:52,220
Today, you are standing together.

71
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:55,940
Perhaps this is
another kind of fulfillment.

72
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,920
(To Shen Gu)

73
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,520
(To Shen Gu)

74
00:04:18,820 --> 00:04:20,340
To Shen Gu.

75
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:27,940
This is the last letter
Miss Lin gave to Mr. Shen.

76
00:04:32,620 --> 00:04:34,820
When the nation is restored,

77
00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:37,580
we shall wed.

78
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:41,280
(From your wife, Shuyi)

79
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:46,940
She knew,

80
00:04:47,740 --> 00:04:48,860
right?

81
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:57,140
From now on, I'm leaving Minghui to you.

82
00:04:58,740 --> 00:05:00,740
No matter what happens,

83
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:05,020
never forget the spirit of Minghui.

84
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:07,420
Create for the people,

85
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:10,220
and serve the prosperity of the nation.

86
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:13,140
Grandfather,

87
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:14,340
don't worry.

88
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:17,540
We will cherish this memory.

89
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:19,980
Grandfather, I'm sorry.

90
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:21,660
During this time,

91
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:23,980
we made you worry.

92
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:31,340
It's good

93
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:34,260
that you're back.

94
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:01,580
Dad,

95
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:04,540
before I propose to Wanxin,

96
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:06,839
I still wanted to ask for your consent.

97
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:08,499
(Tomb of Beloved Father, Xu Zhaoming)

98
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,660
The project you developed
was very successful.

99
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:12,380
It even saved Qingniao.

100
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:15,380
I promise you

101
00:06:15,900 --> 00:06:17,900
that I will love her,

102
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:20,820
protect her, and respect her,
just as you did.

103
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:24,620
And I'll let her always be herself.

104
00:06:27,060 --> 00:06:28,020
Don't worry.

105
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,520
(Grave of Loving Father, Xu Zhaoming)

106
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:44,040
How are the preparations for tonight?

107
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,640
Don't worry about it.

108
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:51,160
Well, you're on your own this time.

109
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:53,040
Don't be too nervous.

110
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,799
Why aren't you talking?

111
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,680
If you're not talking, you're nervous.

112
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,239
What do you need me to do?

113
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,360
Just say the word.

114
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:07,720
I need you to stay out of it.

115
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,880
Okay.

116
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,840
Are you still thinking about
the story Grandfather told?

117
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:13,320
Do you think

118
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,760
there's an afterlife?

119
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,600
If there is an afterlife,

120
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:24,360
we will meet again.

121
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,520
Then, I will recognize you first.

122
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,320
All right.

123
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,160
Let's make a promise.

124
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,000
Before you arrive,

125
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:35,640
I will always wait for you.

126
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,000
It's a deal.

127
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:41,040
If there is an afterlife.

128
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:43,000
Come with me, Wanxin.

129
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,720
Why did you bring me here?

130
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,600
Ms. Xu Wanxin,

131
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,840
are you willing to spend
the rest of your life with me?

132
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,680
I am.

133
00:09:34,690 --> 00:09:40,490
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

134
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:47,570
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

135
00:09:48,290 --> 00:09:53,650
♪You turn and look back at me♪

136
00:09:54,770 --> 00:10:00,290
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

137
00:10:01,130 --> 00:10:06,770
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

138
00:10:08,050 --> 00:10:13,209
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

139
00:10:13,210 --> 00:10:14,649
(To Shen Gu)

140
00:10:14,650 --> 00:10:19,970
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

141
00:10:21,130 --> 00:10:26,930
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

142
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,920
Mr. Shen,

143
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:31,399
a letter has come from Gang City.

144
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,200
Miss Lin has replied.

145
00:10:34,410 --> 00:10:40,090
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

146
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:46,760
(When the nation is restored,
we shall wed. From your wife, Shuyi)

147
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:50,009
♪The promise we made♪

148
00:10:50,010 --> 00:10:53,689
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

149
00:10:53,690 --> 00:11:00,289
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

150
00:11:00,290 --> 00:11:06,690
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

151
00:11:07,090 --> 00:11:13,409
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

152
00:11:13,410 --> 00:11:18,530
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

153
00:11:19,010 --> 00:11:22,010
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪

154
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:25,120
(Shen Hao is convicted of kidnapping,
intentional injury, and insider trading,)

155
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,600
(sentenced to 15 years in prison for
combined crimes, and fined 25 million.)

156
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,840
(Shen Tingyuan, is convicted of insider trading,
sentenced to 5 years and 5 months,)

157
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,360
(and fined 10 million.)

158
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:56,000
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

159
00:11:57,280 --> 00:12:03,080
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

160
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:09,160
♪You turn and look back at me♪

161
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:15,800
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

162
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:22,280
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

163
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:29,040
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

164
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:35,480
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

165
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:42,440
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

166
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:49,800
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

167
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:55,600
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

168
00:12:56,280 --> 00:13:02,639
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

169
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:05,519
♪The promise we made♪

170
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:09,199
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

171
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:15,799
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

172
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:22,200
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

173
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:28,919
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

174
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:34,040
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

175
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:37,520
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
